{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464450/extras/hexa-device.png?t=1731925678\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A 3D platformer in a futuristic world!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to <strong>R Body Adventure</strong>, a 3D platformer focused on adventure set in a futuristic world! In this game, the gameplay evolves progressively throughout the epic journey.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464450/extras/sky-factory.gif?t=1731925678\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Play as R Body and Save the Planet!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take control of <strong>R Body</strong>, an abandoned factory robot who awakens with free will and embarks on an epic journey to save the world from an impending hexagonal fate orchestrated by his own creator, <strong>Mr. Body</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464450/extras/ezgif-1-25c5b8f4a8.gif?t=1731925678\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A Tribute to the Classics</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>R Body Adventure</strong> draws inspiration from classic 3D platformers and &quot;shonen nekketsu&quot; manga, delivering a story-driven experience with a unique visual style. Explore a world where every detail matters and follow an exciting tale full of twists and turns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464450/extras/HighresScreenshot00010.png?t=1731925678\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Hexagonal Rock Project</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mr. Body</strong> has a clear plan: transform the planet into a giant hexagon using the <strong>8 Hexa-devices</strong>. With the countdown already underway, <strong>R Body</strong> must thwart this threat before it\u2019s too late.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464450/extras/plan-mchant-final-dbut-jeu.0593_2-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1731925678\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Flexy, a Worthy Ally</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Luckily, you won\u2019t be alone on this mission. <strong>Flexy</strong>, another defective robot with free will, will join you on this journey. Together, upgrade your components, locate the <strong>8 Hexa-devices</strong> that must be destroyed, and face their tremendous guardians.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464450/extras/flexycoucou.gif?t=1731925678\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A Vast World to Explore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Travel across <strong>Hexa-Earth</strong>, a planet with diverse biomes ranging from mysterious jungles to the stratosphere, passing through the skies and oceans. Encounter various robots, both friend and foe, and face unexpected challenges along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464450/extras/HighresScreenshot00034.png?t=1731925678\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Rich and Varied Experiences</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Launch into a vibrant adventure filled with teleportations, powerful upgrades for <strong>R Body</strong>, and epic battles against colossal bosses. Each level brings surprises and unpredictable events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A great deal of mystery lies within this world \u2014 it\u2019s up to you to uncover it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464450/extras/flipkickmobc-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1731